    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mazzle Halloween is a straightforward yet surprisingly challenging celebration of the simple beauty of mazes and jigsaw puzzles in a Halloween style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you need to skillfully move the puzzle pieces, find their corresponding places, and seamlessly connect the colorful parts of the maze to complete it. Afterward, guide a small ball through the maze, collecting candy corn to unlock the portal to the next level, typically located at the opposite end of the maze.<br><br>Use the mouse to move puzzle pieces and the keyboard (WASD or arrow keys) to navigate through the different mazes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Mazzle Halloween:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 50 levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 5 kinds of labyrinths</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Colorful Halloween art</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Simple controls</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Spooky music</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263590/extras/3c6c19121eac156da0ae6f74c2b0db62.poster.avif?t=1745433656\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263590/extras/3c6c19121eac156da0ae6f74c2b0db62.webm?t=1745433656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
